---
By: Plutarch
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 71
    Verse: 7
Tags:
  - Contentment
---
Learn to be pleased with everything; with wealth, so far as it makes us
beneficial to others; with power, for not having much to care for; and with
obscurity, for being unenvied.
